A VOID BY GEORGES PEREC, 2
now during this time shahrazad had some borne king shahriyar three sons
on the thousand and first night when she had ended the tale of maaruf
she rose and kissed the ground before him saying great king for a
thousand and one nights i have been recounting to you the fables of the past
ages and the legends of ancient kings may i make so bold as to crave a
favour of you majesty

epilogue tales from the thousand and one nights